    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle with a lot of heart? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been a reliable companion and offers a solid foundation for someone looking for a functional ride at a great price. With a little TLC, this car will continue to serve you well for miles to come!",
