    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of uncompromising caliber, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen exhibits no discernible wear, representing the pinnacle of its class through meticulous preservation and rigorous mechanical standards. An acquisition for the discerning driver who demands peak performance and aesthetic perfection. Full provenance and service history are available for review.",
